
1) Git clone this repository with the --recurse-submodules flag

    git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/ealbin/Docker_Cassandra.git

2) Install Docker:

    http://www.docker.com

3a) Use bin/cmd.sh as needed (e.g. boot up/update cassandra)

    bash bin/cmd.sh  (prompted for action)
    bash bin/cmd.sh update  (bypass prompt and go into update mode)

3b) Or use the src/ingest python module directly 
    


(reference: http://hub.docker.com/_/cassandra )
    
